			<div class="content" id="post-content-2525047">
									

<p>This is a thing now.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers&nbsp;-&nbsp;Open&nbsp;after&nbsp;finishing&nbsp;the&nbsp;tale!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;DRINK&nbsp;YOUR&nbsp;OVALTINE</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>This headcanon's been floating about for a while now, i'm just finalising it.</p>
<p>SCP-184 expands the rooms it's contained within.<br />
It's kept outside, and we live in an expanding universe.<br />
After awhile it starts making new rooms, but makes flaws.<br />
Why would the universe be any different? It messes up reality, creating anomalies (Which it further copies.)<br />
Because of this, 184 could very validly be the origin of any and all other anomalies, and the easiest way to hide 001 is to put it in a different slot.<br />
Voilá! SCP-184 is actually SCP-001!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>During the course of working on this, I happened to make some more links and as such, this will be the first in a series. Get excited! More coming soon!</p>
<hr />
<p>Hey look, a <a href="http://scpfoundation.ru/code-name-the-truth">Russian translation</a>! (Cheers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(634139); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=634139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484882011" alt="Gene R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=634139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(634139); return false;">Gene R</a></span>!)<br />
And a <a href="http://ko.scp-wiki.net/code-name-the-truth">Korean translation</a>, courtesy of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xcninety" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1766056); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1766056&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1484882011" alt="XCninety" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1766056)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xcninety" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1766056); return false;">XCninety</a></span>!</p>

