			<div class="content" id="post-content-2713220">
									

<p>I had the first inkling of this idea (SCP-184 = Dark Energy driving the expansion of the Universe) a while ago. But I didn't get all the way to working out the Unfortunate Implications of applying a broken copying machine to the entire universe, so kudos to you. +1</p>
<p>The monster pregnancy is cliched as hell, though. I think something like having the ship run into a really fucked up version of itself might work better. Or having the nav system corrupted in such a way that they are unable to tell which Milky Way to return to. Something more appropriate to the theme of the story.</p>

							</div>

								
					
